attributionInfo.brokerName: KELLER WILLIAMS ISLAND LIFE REAL ESTATE
KELLER WILLIAMS ON THE WATER S

data.description: This charming 3 bedroom home includes a DEN and is available TURNKEY & FURNISHED or Unfurnished. Enjoy the tranquil WATERTONT VIEW from the EXTENDED LANAI. You’ll have peace of mind as the home will come with a one year HOME WARRANTY. Located in WELLEN PARK inside the sought-after Tuscan-inspired Gran Paradiso resort-style community. There are countless upgrades in this 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 2 car garage home, with an OFFICE/DEN. The great room boasts and impressive views from the sliding glass doors. There are TILE FLOORS THROUGHOUT and crown molding in the main living areas. The interior was FRESHLY PAINTED. The gourmet kitchen is complete with granite countertops, cream wood cabinets, backsplash, under cabinet lighting, pull out shelves, an upgraded stainless steel Samsung Refrigerator, and walk in pantry. The master bedroom has his and hers large walk-in closest. The upgraded ensuite bathroom has crown molding, dual sinks, a shower, and a soaking tub. Upgraded lighting and fans have been installed in all rooms. The office/den has double glass doors and the front door is glass as well. The laundry room is complete with upgraded washer and dryer and overhead cabinetry. The 2-car garage comes with epoxy flooring and plenty of room for cars and or a golf cart. This home has an in-the-wall pest control system and digital keyless entry. Rain gutters surround the home. LAWN MAINTENANCE, IRRIGATION, CABLE AND INTERNET are included in the HOA fee. Located in the area only “A” RATED SCHOOL DISTRICT. The Gran Paradiso is a gated, deed-restricted, resort-style community, with on-site management. Among the countless amenities and activities are the community pool, spa, clubhouse, library, meeting rooms, craft room, billiards, ping pong, card room, impressive gym, aerobics room, aerobics classes, sauna, steam room, lockers, tennis, pickle ball, basketball, playground, bike, and golf cart paths, and an extensive calendar of community activities, parties, and events! With over 45 lakes, larger winding roads, lush landscaping, quaint signs, sidewalks, and streetlights. Located within 15-20 minutes of 11 area beaches!! The Gulf of Mexico, Atlanta Braves Stadium, Airports, Many Golf Courses, Shopping, Dining, Venice Theatre, and all the attractions in downtown Venice, Punta Gorda, Wellen Park, and Sarasota are only minutes away.
